Package models

Class FYPCoordinator

java.lang.Object
models.User
models.FYPCoordinator
public class FYPCoordinator extends User
This class represents a FYP Coordinator who can supervise everything in the system. It extends the User class and methods to oversee projects and accept requests. It also has methods to retrieve and update information about the fyp coordinators from the database.
Author:
Timothy Lee, Justin Wong, Jun Hao, Lee Cheng Yao, Abhishekh
